I found a useful refinement: `collectLimOrder()` does not just burn unpaid claims, it also returns and emits the pre-clamp amounts, so integrators can be told they were paid more than they actually received. I’m verifying one last edge case on `pointDelta` before finalizing that fee-tier finding.
